GSILib.BModel

Interface WebResource


  • public interface WebResource
    This is the class WebResource. It's an interface in order to use all the web resources, this is, pictures and webnews.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      boolean addKeyWord(java.lang.String keyword)
      Adds a key word to the list of the associated WebNews

    • Method Detail

      • addKeyWord

        boolean addKeyWord(java.lang.String keyword)
        Adds a key word to the list of the associated WebNews
        Parameters:
        keyword - keyword to input into the web notice.
        Returns:
        true if key word is smaller than 6 characters, and is added to the associated WebNews correctly, false otherwise.

      • getUrl

        java.lang.String getUrl()
        Retrieves the information on the URL of a Picture. If the Picture is not stored in the system, the result is null.
        Returns:
        The URL associated with the picture

      • getAutor

        Photographer getAutor()
        Retrieves the information on the author of a Picture. If the Picture is not stored in the system, the result is null.
        Returns:
        The photographer associated with the picture
